data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home on a quiet culdesac located in the Deep Creek community. This home boast a spacious living area with a cathedral ceiling.  The kitchen features wood cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a wine cabinet over the refridgerator. The living, kitchen and dinning area is an open concept. The owners bedroom is on the north side of the home with walk in double closets and sliding doors that lead to the patio area. The on suite bathroom has double sinks, lots of counter space and a walk in shower. The additional bedrooms are on the south side of the home with the bathroom in between and a hallway to give true privacy. The back of the home has true Florida charm with a large enclosed patio. Beautiful landscaping surrounds the home. Roof was recently replaced.  The home is located close to I-75, shopping and restaurants. Seller will contribute $5,000 to buyers closing cost.
